      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this beauty to believe it. It's in absolutely stunning, showroom-ready condition and has been pampered since day one. It drives like a dream and looks virtually brand new inside and out. If you've been looking for that perfect ride that feels like it just rolled off the lot, this is definitely the one for you! Let's get you behind the wheel!",
