    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the legendary S54 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six delivers linear power through six individual throttle bodies, with the double-VANOS system fully serviced and operating flawlessly. This unit features a factory-reinforced rear subframe and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The suspension geometry is optimized with Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, ensuring razor-sharp turn-in and high-speed stability. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains its factory luster with zero oxidation, while the undercarriage remains concours-clean. A mechanically transparent, investment-grade driver for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
