    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, meticulously maintained to the highest standards by a single enthusiast owner. The exterior retains its showroom luster with a deep, mirror-like finish, completely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in factory-fresh condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no visible wear, and every electronic feature operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach\u2014always garage-kept, never driven in inclement weather, and strictly serviced at authorized intervals. Included with the sale are all original keys, a complete set of stamped service records, and the original owner's manuals. If you are seeking a collector-grade example that drives as perfectly as it looks, this is an unparalleled opportunity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
